X_k = (X_{k-1} * 1.4) - 230
-230
y_k=X_k+n
n
y_k-n=1.4(y_{k-1}-n)-230\\y_k=1.4y_{k-1}-1.4n+n-230\\y_k=1.4y_{k-1}-230-0.4n
n=-\frac {230}{0.4}=-575
y_k=1.4^ky_0
X_k=1.4^k(X_0-575)+575
x_k
x_k - a x_{k-1} = b
x_k^{(H)}
x_k^{(I)}
x_k^{(H)}
x_k^{(H)} = C a^k
C
x_k^{(I)}
x_k^{(I)} = A k +B
A k +B - a (A (k-1) + B) = A (1-a) k + B(1-a) + A a = b
A=0
B = b/(1-a)
x_k = C a^k + \frac{b}{1-a}
a=1.4
b=-230
